description: This common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 38, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 114, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Nine Lives for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [114 Votes, Common]
